<table class="wrapper" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td class="px-sm-16" align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
      <table class="container" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="600">
        <tr>
          <td class="px-sm-8" align="left" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="padding: 0 24px">
            <div class="spacer line-height-sm-0 py-sm-8" style="line-height: 24px">&zwnj;</div>
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="100%">
              <tr>
                <td class="col px-sm-16" align="left" width="100%" style="padding: 0 64px">
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 48px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" width="60%">
                    <tr>
                      <td class="col" align="left" width="100%">
                        <a href="https://biz.iwannabetter.com">
                          <img src="https://iwannabetter.com/logo/logo1.png" alt="Header Logo" width="60%" />
                        </a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <h2 style="color: #888888; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 28px; margin: 0 0 24px">
                    Hi <%= email %>,
                  </h2>
                  <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0">
                    비밀번호 변경을 요청하여 아래와 같이 비밀번호 변경 링크를 보내드립니다.<br /><br />아래 링크를
                    선택하시고 웹사이트에서 비밀번호를 변경하세요 <br /><br />
                  </p>
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        class="webfont hover-scale"
                        bgcolor="#32B38A"
                        style="border-radius: 3px; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; mso-padding-alt: 6px 32px 12px"
                      >
                        <a
                          href="<%= url %>"
                          style="
                            color: #ffffff;
                            display: inline-block;
                            font-size: 14px;
                            font-weight: 700;
                            padding: 12px 32px;
                            text-decoration: none;
                          "
                          >비밀번호변경</a
                        >
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <br />

                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <p style="color: #999999; margin: 0">
                    비밀번호 변경을 원하지 않으시는 경우 이 이메일을 무시하셔도 괜찮습니다.
                  </p>
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0">
                    Thanks, <br />
                    WANNAB Team
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="spacer line-height-sm-0 py-sm-8" style="line-height: 24px">&zwnj;</div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
